<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رَوى عنهُ كِلابُ بنُ عَديٍّ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[١٠٦٩٠]</span> مَنصورُ بنُ عَبدِ اللَّهِ <span class="c2">(٥)</span> بنِ الأَحْوصِ، القُرشِيُّ <span class="c2">(٦)</span> <span class="c2">(٧)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مِن بَني عَبدِ شَمْسٍ <span class="c2">(٨)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
